values.text: Superstar rookie, as a freshman he's already Shohoku's ace. His offensive prowess is...
values.value: Superstar rookie, as a freshman he's already Shohoku's ace. His offensive prowess is mind-blowing, being able to score in the paint, from downtown and anywhere in between. He shines the most in 1-on-1 situations. Sleeping is his hobby. Sakuragi's rival and the object of Haruko's affection, but he couldn't care any less. Sakuragi calls him fox.
values.creator: /user/daepark
